{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_05_01",
  "title": "白石沙季 1話 意外な一面を探して",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、沙季も練習お疲れ様\nちょうど仕事の話をしたかったんだ。少しだけいいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Saki‚ good job with the practice too.\nI wanted to talk about work. Can you spare a moment?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです\nどんなお仕事ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course.\nWhat kind of work is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "雑誌の特集で「アイドルの日常」という\n記事を組むことになったらしくてな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems they want to feature an article\nin a magazine called \"Idols' Daily Lives.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それで、星見プロでも特に真面目な沙季なら「意外な\n一面があるかもしれないから」と声が掛かったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They thought that if it's you‚ Saki‚ who's particularly serious‚\nthere might be \"unexpected aspects\" they can capture.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "そういう理由で声が掛かることもあるんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So they approached me with that kind of reason.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.0333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3733.333333400001,
          "startTime": 28.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "えっと企画内容が……『仕事の時だけでなく\n休日の姿もなるべく等身大で伝えたい』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So the contents are…\n\"We want to convey your daily life as realistically as possible‚ not just during work hours.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "『そのため、関係者が写真を撮影したりメモを\n残したりして、それを基に記事を書く』……なるほど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"For that purpose‚ the staff will take photos and leave notes as they interact with you‚\nand then we will write the article based on that.\" I see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "この場合の『関係者』というと……\n{user}さんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In this case‚ the \"staff\" would be\n… {user}-san‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことになるな\n沙季さえ良ければ、なんだけど。どうだろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's how it seems.\nIf it's okay with you‚ Saki‚ how about it? What do you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "私はぜひともお願いしたいですが……\n{user}さんが大変では？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I would love to do it‚ but…\nWouldn't it be troublesome for you‚ {user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "沙季のことをより深く知れる機会だからな\n同行させてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's an opportunity to get to know you better‚ Saki.\nLet me accompany you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さんがそう言うなら\n分かりました、よろしくお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…If {user}-san says so.\nUnderstood. I'll count on you then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Few days later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.9
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、休日にもかかわらず\n付き合っていただきありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ {user}-san‚\nfor spending time with me on your day off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "あら？\nその、首に下げたカメラは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh?\nWhat's that camera hanging around your neck?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、これは事務所から持って来たんだ\n撮影はスマホでもいいらしいんだけど、せっかくだしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I brought this from the office.\nThey said it's fine to use a smartphone‚ I thought it'd be a waste…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ{user}さんがカメラを持つ姿は……\nなんだかちょっと初々しいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ seeing {user}-san holding a camera…\nIt feels kind of charming and endearing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "からかわないでくれ……まぁ、カメラは不慣れでも\n沙季の魅力はきっちり捉えるから安心してくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't tease me… Well‚ even if I'm not good with the camera‚\nI'll capture your charm perfectly‚ so don't worry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですか。……よろしくお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-Right. …Thank you for that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "それで、今日なんですが\nまず初めに読書をしようと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ for today…\nFirst‚ I thought of doing some reading.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "元々私、文芸作品が好きなんですが\n最近はミステリーも読んでいて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've always liked literature‚\nbut recently I've been reading mysteries too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんオススメの料理本や、瑠依さんと\n愛ちゃんから聞いた体作りの本も読み始めました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san recommended some cooking books‚ and I started reading\nbooks about body improvement based on what Rui-san and Ai-chan told me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "みんなのおかげで、読書の幅が広がってるんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to everyone‚ your reading interests have expanded.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね、世界が広がる感覚はとても楽しいです\n後は……あ、そういえば",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. It's really exciting to have the world expand before you.\nAlso‚ by the way…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "最近は渚ちゃんが好きな\n大人な恋愛小説も読んでいるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Recently‚ I've been reading the\nmature romance novels that Nagisa likes too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "以前は過激な描写のたびに気絶してしまい、渚ちゃんが\nすっかり私の介抱に慣れてしまったんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the past‚ I used to faint from the explicit content‚\nand Nagisa got used to taking care of me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
